--[[ 
  ModzRO - Full Read-Only Menu (Vietnamese)
  - Paste vÃ o KRNL and run in-game (Blox Fruits)
  - Read-only: hiá»ƒn thá»‹ realtime info, map, sá»± kiá»‡n, danh sÃ¡ch boss (xanh=alive, Ä‘á»=dead)
  - KhÃ´ng thay Ä‘á»•i CFrame, khÃ´ng teleport, khÃ´ng auto-farm
